Author: javmarfer
Title: 🔵☄️🔵 [ANN][ICO]VRT.WORLD - VR WORLD IN ONE TECHNOLOGY 🔵☄️🔵
Body: The VRT WORLD investment opportunity will be extended with a third round of fundraising for private investors and funds of $50,000 and higher. In order to reach and surpass the token sale soft cap of $3,430,000, this opportunity will be available until July 30 or the moment VRT successfully concludes all current dealings.  The team is working with a number of funds and private investors at this time. As the VRT team works to finalize pre-arrangements with these investors and funds, everyone will have more time to learn more about the VRT Project and to take advantage of this great investment opportunity.  At this time, VRT has not reached the soft cap of $3,430,000, so the team is working with private investors to raise that minimum needed to develop all plans for the future. The hard cap is $16 million. With that in mind, the team will offer a private fundraising round following the token sale for investors and large funds. During this special sale—June 1 to July 30—VRT plans to raise a total of $1,5 million with participation from the $50,000 funds. The target is $1.5 million USD overall.  BTC, ETH, BCASH, DASH and LTC currencies are accepted, and tokens purchased via ETH will be distributed to participant wallets on the Ethereum blockchain, with a balance closed in smart contracts. All funds raised are received and saved in multi-signature wallets. Each VRT token is equivalent to $1 USD.  The team will continue to update the community on the progress of development as current investment dealings are finalized. Meanwhile, VRT will continue to develop the VRT WORLD platform and virtual reality park franchise, which are already up and running. Additionally, the team is working on new content and knows that everyone in the VRT community will be excited about this quality material and further project development.

Author: semsyor
Title: 🔵☄️🔵 [ANN][ICO]VRT.WORLD - VR WORLD IN ONE TECHNOLOGY 🔵☄️🔵
Body: New VR-headset — Oculus Go and HTC Vive Pro  There are dozens of virtual reality headsets presented in the market for the moment — from budget models that work in conjunction with a smartphone, to advanced ones, for which a PC game is needed. Soon the situation can dramatically change — powerful headsets will be deprived of associated equipment and will cease to constrain users. The first steps in this direction have already been made — today let us talk about Oculus Go and HTC Vive Pro.  Oculus Go  Oculus Rift is perhaps the most famous VR headset on the market. Everyone have heard of it after Facebook bought Oculus VR for more than $ 2 billion.  The consumer version of the Oculus Rift went on sale in March 2016, the Oculus Touch controllers in December of the same year. Facebook does not disclose how many devices was sold, but on Steam (the largest online gaming store) there are about 70 thousand owners of Rift. True, it is worth adding that Oculus VR is developing its own store of VR-applications — Oculus Store.  At CES 2018 Facebook presented Oculus Go — a light version of Rift with a price of $ 200 instead of $ 600. Oculus Go do not need an external computing node (PC) or a smartphone. At the same time, the resolution of the picture is 2560x1440 against 2160x1200 at Rift. Additional characteristics are not provided, but the concept of a cheaper and self-contained headset is impressive. In China, by the way, Xiaomi will produce a copy of the Oculus Go — Mi VR Standalone (with 32 or 64 GB of flash memory).  Jason Rubin, one of the leaders of Oculus VR, in a recent interview honestly outlined the minuses of Rift — insufficient resolution, solid weight and a requirement to use in conjunction with the PC. In fairness, these are technical disadvantages, not conceptual ones. Oculus VR is aimed at high-quality graphics, a wide field of view and, of course, the lack of additional wires. Partially named ideas are embodied in the Go helmet.  A promising development of Facebook is the Oculus Santa Cruz glasses, summarizing the power of Rift with Go mobility. This device is “all in one”.  It is noteworthy that Facebook cares not only about the hardware, but also about the creators of content. In January 2018, the Start program was announced, aimed at novice developers under the VR. Participation is free of charge. Companies registered in the program will open access to products (including Oculus Santa Cruz), and to technologies.  https://medium.com/@VRTOKEN/new-vr-headset-oculus-go-and-htc-vive-pro-e7ff197be23c

Author: Toltekayotl
Title: 🔵☄️🔵 [ANN][ICO]VRT.WORLD - VR WORLD IN ONE TECHNOLOGY 🔵☄️🔵
Body: From the article: Quote VRT World independently produces active markers, which can be recognized by the frequency in the flicker of the diodes. In this case, there are eight of them, and this gives amazingly accurate tracking to a millimeter of a separate movement. In this case, each active label can be assigned its own algorithm of operation. They are not tied to a specific geometry.  Active markers have advantages in production. Microchips for markers (as well as lenses and cameras) are supplied by Optitrack, a long-established manufacturer. Microcomputers in MSI backpacks with MSI VR ONE replaceable batteries transfer data to virtual reality glasses. The glasses can be of any brand but the preference is given to the VR-helmet Oculus. As a result, the total weight of all the equipment that a player wears for participation is significantly reduced in comparison with analogues.  Perhaps most importantly, the fact that several participants are able to interact in virtual reality is realized, which VRT World’s Full-Body Tracking VR technology gives in full, and this is the impetus for the active development of eSports and collective travel. Note that participants can be in different countries even. The marks of active players on the soles of their feet, wrists, and back ate tracked by the cameras, and the movements of the main parts of the body are calculated and completed according to the reverse kinematics algorithm. The algorithm is based on the knowledge of human anatomy and calculates the rotation of the joints. The company took great efforts, carried out intensive research and shooting of movements in order to confidently create this leading innovative program. Any turn is immediately transferred to the virtual world and naturally fits into it, and is also visible to other participants.  Very cool article. I am very glad that such developments are being conducted in Russia. I hope in a couple of years your VR-park will be known to the whole world.  Quote The ability to play 1.5 hours without stopping, the powerful Core i7 7700HQ processor and the GTX1070 graphics card, the hot battery replacement, the weight of just 3.5 kg and the comfortable suspension system are surely the best in the world! It seems to me that the video card is rather weak. I would put there two video cards GeForce GTX TITAN X SLI. It will be possible to play with 4K resolution

The entertainment industry is optimally suited for this. Many of you have seen the VR-parks in small towns? I - the most of any roller coaster or skydiving in the Oculus Rift. Year through 2-3-4 we will see VR-parks in almost every city. The explosive growth of miniaturization, and therefore cheaper batteries and computer systems will in the near future to use VR at home, or most approximate to them. And at this moment all of competitors will be able to survive and provide a qualitative growth of the one who will create the ecosystem for the development and commercialization of new solutions in VR\AR. SDK should solve this problem and the marketplace for solutions built on this SDK will allow to commercialize VR-objects, games, educational programs from third party developers.

Title: 🔵☄️🔵 [ANN][ICO]VRT.WORLD - VR WORLD IN ONE TECHNOLOGY 🔵☄️🔵
Body: Hi! If you the part of blockchain in out project: We use blockchain to distribute the profit between the project participants (developers and customers), to respect the copyright of the developers, for the correct and fair operation of our franchise, for voting on the platform and much more (more details are written on the site in the Blockchain section). If you mean why we do token sale and not a conventional venture capital investment: Because we want that the community, which is one of the most important components of the project was the organizers and its immediate creators. That's why we use Blockchain, which involves the work of an internal token with which you can work on the platform and go to the parks. To buy content and much more . We want VRT to remain an independent high-tech project without pressure from investors who are not directly interested in the development of VR!

Author: willoweb
Title: 🔵☄️🔵 [ANN][ICO]VRT.WORLD - VR WORLD IN ONE TECHNOLOGY 🔵☄️🔵
Body: For me, your project was the first ICO project based on VR technology and the blockchain. I invested tangible, for my budget the amount of funds in the project, being confident in his success. Before taking such a decision, I spent a week studying the white paper, site, team and advisors, competitors, asking questions, sometimes perhaps uncomfortable. Before taking the decision to participate in your ICO, I read a lot of material in the web and agree with the analysts that VR is one of the most promising technologies of the future. It will take a couple of years and the development of technologies will allow to miniaturise all the elements necessary for a complete immersion in virtual reality, their cost will decrease and the technology of virtual / augmented reality will be available to all. Possible neural interfaces in the near future will replace the existing ways of interaction with virtual reality. And these technologies are now at the stage of entering the market. In the near future virtual reality will be a huge multi-billion dollar market allowing to immerse yourself in virtual reality at home, and will be the impuls of development for various types of business: medicine, education, space exploration and other spheres, which we don't even know now. And those companies who begin to popularize virtual reality will become the leaders of this emerging market. I sincerely wish success to the project team and everyone who, like me, believe in the development of virtual reality. I do not exclude that after 3-4-5 years Google or Facebook will acquire the technology and achievements of vrt.world for tens of billions of dollars.

Body: Hello! To motivate VR employees, as well as developers, very specific people and to build a strong team is not the easiest task. We keep part of the tokens for further bonuses and for motivating the team. 3% of tokens are reserved for further exchange in the network of Bancor’s through their smart tokens.How it works in reality - we put our tokens on the Bancor's purse, they are evaluated by their algorithm and they are exposed to the price relative to the internal token (the Bancor's token) About the reserve for our team: it will be frozen for a year and will be gradually distributed among between advisors and emploees. It's important that there is no situation that this reserve splashes into the stock exchange in one day and discards the course.

Author: javmarfer
Title: 🔵☄️🔵 [ANN][ICO]VRT.WORLD - VR WORLD IN ONE TECHNOLOGY 🔵☄️🔵
Body: Hello! Of course not, we have three huge parts of platform: SDK (soft developer kit) - for VR content developers. The main idea of the kit to make possible develop any VR content and emulate it for different kind of glasses (oculus, vive, Samsung etc). We have a lot of assets for parks (system call full body tracking) and give developers them to use it. Market place - it's like a Apple Store or google play but for VR. VR Parks - we see the dynamics (see the VR/AR research of super data company) and understand, that VR will grow but we should to help the market and make it possible to try VR everybody.  Hope you know why we use blockchain (distribution of profits, copyrights etc). All small and middle game dev have a problem with it and blockchain will solve lots of problems.  In this case, VR PARK is just one of the parts and reason to believe of our expertise.
